      "text": [
        " «أَصَّدَّقَ مِنَ اَلصَّدَقَةِ «وَ أَكُنْ مِنَ اَلصّٰالِحِينَ» أَيْ أَحُجَّ»."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2228 - He was asked about the words of Allah (swt), Mighty and Majestic: \"So I will give in charity and be among the righteous\" (Surah Al-Munafiqun 63:10).\nImam (as) said: \"'I will give in charity' refers to giving charity, and 'be among the righteous' means performing Hajj.\""
        ]
      }
